<quantity box="[813,912,883,907]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="10" pageNumber="803" unit="mm" value="100.0">100 mm</quantity>
long, only one with a couple of hydrocladia (
<collectionCode box="[412,501,915,939]" country="USA" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34871" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34871" name="Smithsonian Institution, National Museum of Natural History" pageId="10" pageNumber="803" type="Museum">USNM</collectionCode>
1025574); 
<emphasis box="[643,747,915,939]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="803">731/1944</emphasis>
